org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.ucm.supplement.profile.UCM_Supplement.ucm_detailed_components

Interface Ucm_detailed_componentsPackage

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EModelElement, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.ENamedElement, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EPackage, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Ucm_detailed_componentsPackageImpl

    public interface Ucm_detailed_componentsPackage
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EPackage
    The Package for the model. It contains accessors for the meta objects to represent
    • each class,
    • each feature of each class,
    • each operation of each class,
    • each enum,
    • and each data type
    See Also:
    Ucm_detailed_componentsFactory
